headline: My 2 Favorite Stocks to Buy Right Now
summary: Hershey is deeply out of favor for good reasons, but it is also offering a historically high yield.  Realty Income is trading near 10-year high yields and is operating just as well as always.  No company goes through its life without facing adversity.
